Package: pomodoro-lock
Version: 1.2.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Vinay Gundala <vg@ivdata.dev>
Installed-Size: 274
Depends: python3, python3-venv, python3-gi, python3-notify2, python3-dbus, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/vgundala/pomodoro-lock
Description: Multi-display Pomodoro timer with screen overlay
 A comprehensive Pomodoro timer application that helps you maintain focus during
 work sessions and enforces breaks with full-screen overlays across all
 connected displays.
 .
 This package installs the application in userspace with a virtual environment,
 eliminating the need for system-wide Python package installation.
 .
 Features include:
  - Standalone UI with integrated timer and overlay functionality
  - Desktop notifications before break periods
  - Multi-display screen overlays during breaks
  - System tray integration with AppIndicator3
  - Configurable work/break cycles
  - Automatic startup via systemd user service
 .
 It runs as a user service and is designed to be compatible with
 most modern desktop environments.
